title: Maxwell Silver Trender 10/20: Nick Rolovich, Child Vaccination, Ted Sarandos, Joe Manchin, 'Fuck Joe Biden', Being the Ricardos
itunes:title: Maxwell Silver Trender 10/20: Nick Rolovich, Child Vaccination, Ted Sarandos, Joe Manchin, 'Fuck Joe Biden', Being the Ricardos
description:
In this edition of Maxwell Silver Trender, Jack and Miles discuss Nick Rolovich fucking around and finding out, Biden's child vaxx plans coming into focus, Ted Sarandos addressing Dave Chappelle's fallout, the rumors around Joe Manchin going indie, Soxx fans chanting 'Fuck Joe Biden', Wu Tang's one-of-a-kind album being sold for $4 million, and the trailer for 'Being the Ricardos'.
